== Provinces == {{Main|Provinces of Nepal}}[[File:Province Map of Nepal.svg|thumb|Map of Nepal With 7 Provinces]] Nepal is composed of seven provinces.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://foreignpolicynews.org/2015/10/24/nepal-divided-by-new-constitution/|title=Nepal divided by new constitution - Foreign Policy News|website=foreignpolicynews.org|language=en-US|access-date=2018-04-07}}</ref> They are defined by schedule 4 of the new [[Constitution of Nepal|constitution]], by grouping together the existing [[List of districts of Nepal|districts]]. Two districts however are split in two parts ending up in two different provinces.
