==Olmsted Brothers== After the retirement of Frederick Law Olmsted Sr in 1895, the firm was managed by [[John Charles Olmsted]] and [[Frederick Law Olmsted Jr.]], as Olmsted and Olmsted, Olmsted Olmsted and [[Charles Eliot (landscape architect)|Eliot]], and [[Olmsted Brothers]]. Works from this period are often misattributed to Frederick Sr.
