This is a list of the '''[[Extreme points of Earth|extreme points]] of [[Latvia]]''': the points that are farther north, south, east or west than any other location.

== Latitude and longitude ==

* North : ({{coord|58.085137|25.199204|type:landmark_region:LV|display=inline}}) [[Rūjiena municipality]], [[Ipiķi parish]]
* South : ({{coord|55.674971|26.597214|type:landmark_region:LV|display=inline}}) [[Daugavpils municipality]], [[Demene parish]]
* West : ({{coord|56.353934|20.970154|type:landmark_region:LV|display=inline}}) [[Nīca municipality]], [[Nīca parish]]
* East : ({{coord|56.276911|28.241043|type:landmark_region:LV|display=inline}}) [[Zilupe municipality]], [[Pasiene parish]]

== Altitude ==
* Maximum : [[Gaiziņkalns]] ({{coord|56.870134|25.95751|type:landmark_region:LV|display=inline}}), 312 meters
* Minimum : sea level, 0 meters

